{"tid":340542,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★[片]女主播主持期間　突然兩眼反白倒地","createTime":"2017-07-30T05:03:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-30T11:58:10.000Z","uid":19454,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"29d936a8bbc0de71d888a611074e93d090f1ca68","tid":340542,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T05:03:45.000Z","msg":"[url]<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bmo2HPOIH5Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dbmo2HPOIH5Q&d=gubv%2FZ0EvCqiM1c4DTtkV49%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=962ac3e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bmo2HPOIH5Q</a><br />\n[/url]<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170726/large/1501081505_51b4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170726%2Flarge%2F1501081505_51b4.jpg&h=8ffca024&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n驚嚇！26日下午起網傳一段短片，顯示一名美女主持人張涵在主持節目時，在台上突然兩眼反白、拗腰倒下，倒地瞬間表情僵硬，看上去是突發疾病。網上爆料者聲稱是河北「邯鄲電視台新聞主播，工作中突遇心梗，年僅26歲」。<br />\n從事發現場背景顯示，當時女主持正在主持由邯鄲市委宣傳部主辦的「最美邯鄲人發佈廳」，該活動昨日（26日）在邯鄲廣播電視台演播廳發佈，並表彰10名「最美環保衞士」和10名「最美保安」。<br />\n其後，據「邯鄲網絡廣播電視台」官方微博回應稱，目前該女主持已沒有大礙。據悉女主持當時是因低血糖暈倒，休息後已重投工作。"},{"pid":"ccf816206c2047fdee8c95535e63943a02728b1f","tid":340542,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T05:04:39.000Z","msg":"玩乜？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41f338ea9b44c7871d25af9a64a056c59ce75641","tid":340542,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T05:06:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170727/57006331\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170727%2F57006331&d=gubv%2FZ0EvCqiM1c4DTtkV49%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=c104ba41\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frea